  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 1st level, members of the Akushū clan possess an unfortunate characteristic where their exhaled breath carries toxic fumes. To counteract this, the clan utilizes specialized breathing masks, preventing</p><p>the harmful effects of their breath. While wearing your</p><p>Gas Mask, you gain immunity to jutsu or conditions</p><p>caused by inhalation. Your mask is custom-fitted for</p><p>you, and if it breaks or is lost, you can fashion a</p><p>replacement during a Long Rest by spending</p><p>250 ryo, given access to a workshop during</p><p>this period.</p>",
